        datosHistoricos_en: `Pandebono has its origins in Afro-Colombian communities of the Pacific coast, who prepared corn and cassava dumplings. Its current version with cheese was perfected in Valle del Cauca in the late 19th century. The first bakeries in downtown Cali date from the 1910s, when the city was experiencing the cotton and coffee commerce boom.`,
