        datosHistoricos_en: `The first interventions on the Cali River walls were carried out informally by graffiti collectives in the 1990s. Starting in 2010, the Cali Mayor's Office institutionalized the process through FAUC (Cali Urban Art Festival), turning the interventions into official commissions to recognized artists.`,
